          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="37346092">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cafince/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49713415-14.jpg" alt="飞飞哥" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37346092/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37346092/" class="">第107页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cafince/" class=" " title="飞飞哥">飞飞哥</a>
                (当你的海，就不会在意你没有岸)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37346092">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">真正的平等不是以同样的标准对待每个人，而是对每个人的不同需要给予同等的关注。而这才是马克思希望建立的那种社会。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-03-10 14:23</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                真正的平等不是以同样的标准对待每个人，而是对每个人的不同需要给予同等的关注。而这才是马克思希望建立的那种社会。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37346092/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2016-03-10 14:23
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
